Chancellor: The time for the royal bloodline's awakening is
near! If you intend to interfere with my plans, I will show
no mercy──!
Having come this far... am I still not enough...

Chancellor: Even as a knight, in the end, a woman is just a
woman.

Chancellor: I acknowledge that you've made it this far even
wounded, and I shall take you into my service.

Chancellor: Do your best. As an unconscious battle doll,
that is.
